item.title: Farland Epic server 317 Need staff!
item.dc:creator: @xEthanx xEthanx
item.description:
@xEthanx wrote:

It appears that isn’t even his own site, but just another site that’s supposed to run his webclient for him. Which they failed at doing so, because the page he linked doesn’t exist.

He’s right though dude. You need pictures. Did you even get those two links verified by a staff member before posting this? My baby cousin could’ve typed this in 5 minutes. Make it appealing or no one will want to come. It’s also kind of odd how you just list off all your features in one sentence. Try spreading them out a little with pictures for each?

I also find it rather retarded that your client title is “Farland||WHERE WE SMOKE WEED OG KUSH FROM THE WEST COAST”… You’re impressing no one and it just looks stupid.

It’s also worth pointing out that these graphics aren’t actually 317. Not sure of their specific revision but they aren’t. Not a 317 cache anyway. You should at least get that right.
